text: Kurt Heyndrickx (born 30 August 1972) is a Belgian equestrian. He competed in the team eventing at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Belgium Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:People from Sint-Niklaas
